OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,6,Fdry day. Cloudier in the morning with
OL,7,Fjust the slight chance of an isolated
OL,8,Flight shower. Increasingly sunny
OL,9,Fspells developing through the day.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly dry with some bright
OL,13,For sunny spells and variable cloud in
OL,14,Fthe evening. Turning cloudier
OL,15,Fovernight with a few light showers.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FBright spells and variable
OL,18,Fcloud with the odd light shower in the
OL,19,Fmorning. Drier for a time around the
OL,20,Fmiddle of the day before rain spreads
OL,21,Feast from late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
